lead_paragraph: New England coach Eddie Jones defended his "conservative" first team on Thursday after naming an experienced lineup to face Scotland in the Six Nations in Edinburgh on Saturday and keeping his uncapped trio on the bench.

headline.print_headline: Jones Defends New England's Old Look
headline.main: Jones Defends New England's Old Look
